<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.3">
<l>kāyunīr pukkuk kaṭampēṟik kāḷiyaṉ</l>
<l>tīya paṇattiṟ cilampārkkap pāyntāṭi</l>
<l>vēyiṉ kuḻalūti vittaka ṉāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>vāyaṉvan tappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Entering the hot water, climbing the Cadamba tree,</l>
<l>leaping and dancing on Kāḷiya’s fiery hood</l>
<l>so that [his] anklets rang out, blowing [his] bamboo flute,</l>
<l>the cowherd who stood as the wonderous one</l>
<l>comes and is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
